# Prompt Engineering Guide

## System Prompt Strategy
Defines:
- Tone
- Role
- Output structure

Example:
"You are a structured AI technical documentation assistant."

## Context Handling
- Maintains conversation history
- Uses role-based message formatting

## Parameter Recommendations

| Use Case | Temperature | Top_p |
|----------|------------|-------|
| Technical Writing | 0.3–0.7 | 0.8–0.95 |
| Creative Content | 0.8–1.2 | 0.9–1.0 |
